snippet.title: Punch Club 2 - Official Announcement Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Punch Club 2 is coming to PS5 and PS4 in 2023.

It’s bigger. It’s better. It’s in the FUTURE! Fight your way to discover the darkest secrets of your family and the entire City in a smashing sequel to the management tycoon -Punch Club.

#ps4 #ps4games #ps5 #ps5games
